---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Backend Engineer" description="My background, experience, and technical stack.">
  
  <section class="prose prose-slate prose-lg dark:prose-invert mb-16 max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
      About Me
    </h1>
    <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
      I am a Software Engineer with a focus on <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Distributed Systems</strong> and <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Cloud Infrastructure</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      I don't just write code; I design systems that are reliable, scalable, and maintainable. 
      My philosophy is simple: <strong>boring technology is better technology</strong>. 
      I prefer proven solutions (Postgres, Linux) over hype, and I believe that clear documentation is just as important as clean code.
    </p>
    <p>
      Currently, I am working on high-throughput payment processing systems. Before that, 
      I helped scale a monolithic architecture into microservices for a fintech startup.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg>
      The Stack
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Languages</h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Java (Spring Boot)", "Go (Golang)", "Python", "Rust", "TypeScript"].map((item) => (
            <li class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 rounded-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Data & Messaging</h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["PostgreSQL", "Redis", "Kafka", "Elasticsearch", "RabbitMQ"].map((item) => (
            <li class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 rounded-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Infrastructure</h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Docker", "Kubernetes", "AWS (EC2, Lambda, S3)", "Terraform", "GitHub Actions"].map((item) => (
            <li class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 rounded-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Tools & Workflow</h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Git", "Neovim / VS Code", "Linux", "Postman", "Grafana", "Prometheus"].map((item) => (
            <li class="px-3 py-1 text-sm bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 rounded-md border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path></svg>
      Experience
    </h2>

    <div class="relative border-l border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 ml-3 space-y-12">
      
      <div class="relative pl-8">
        <span class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-400 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-[#0B1120]"></span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Senior Backend Engineer</h3>
        <span class="text-sm font-mono text-slate-500">TechCorp • 2021 - Present</span>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
          Leading the migration from a PHP monolith to Go microservices. Improved system latency by 40% and implemented a new event-driven architecture using Kafka.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-8">
        <span class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-slate-300 dark:bg-slate-600 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-[#0B1120]"></span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Software Engineer</h3>
        <span class="text-sm font-mono text-slate-500">StartupInc • 2018 - 2021</span>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
          Built the initial payment gateway integration using Python/Django. Designed the REST API consumed by the mobile team.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>